com.ibm.itim.script

Interface ScriptInterface

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AttributesScriptInterface, DelegateScriptInterface, EmailContextScriptInterface, IdentityPolicyScriptInterface, LoopCountScriptInterface, ModelScriptInterface, PersonPlacementRulesScriptInterface, PostOfficeScriptInterface, ProvisioningPolicyScriptInterface, ReminderScriptInterface, ServiceScriptInterface, SubjectScriptInterface, WorkflowScriptInterface

    public interface ScriptInterface
    This is the top-level interface of all ScriptInterfaces. Each ScriptExtension defines a ScriptInterface that any class wanting to use that extension must implement.
    Since:
    ITIM 5.0
